'''Brett Brady''' (1952 - December 11, 2018) was an American fighter pilot in the United States Air Force. 

==Service==
Brett enlisted in 1970 during the Vietnam War. 

... 

Brady retired from active duty in 2014.

==Personal life==
Brady was married twice and fathered five children. He died on December 11, 2018. He is survived by his five children and seven grandchildren. 

